  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>Restaurant Le Gourmet offers refined cuisine showcasing some of the best ingredients on the Neapolitan Riviera. It’s lovely terrace enjoys wonderful sea views and there’s an extensive wine list with both local and international labels.</p>
<p>There are two bars at the hotel with sea views and a large choice of drinks.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>There are three pools to choose from at Grand Hotel Punta Molino including one freshwater pool next to the sea, one outdoor thermal pool and one indoor thermal pool in the spa. Outdoor pools are open seasonally.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s spa offers innovative treatments and uses mud therapy and thermal waters. There’s also a fully-equipped gym.</p>]]></facilityDescription>
