  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>measure 25m<sup>2 </sup>and have views of the park from a window. Finished in a Mediterranean style, each room has air conditioning, TV, free wifi, minibar, safe and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>are up to 30m<sup>2 </sup>and have a French balcony. They’re located either in the main building or the tower with either park or sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>offer plenty of space with 35m<sup>2 </sup>and have a furnished balcony overlooking the sea.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
